了過來。&quot;藥力過左之後又死唔去應該都好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪co- potassium 囉"},{"pid":"50d4d52ebd9d5adc4d6b067b4628abcc4d8322b8","tid":261524,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解死刑犯就以人道理由無痛死亡<br />\n但係就好多地有唔比人安樂死<br />\n普通人仲慘過死刑犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=znF4YjxlH08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DznF4YjxlH08&d=4Baf2qCrSLdHTNG60W%2FfEJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=46da82d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=znF4YjxlH08</a>"},{"pid":"31d29f67ff1135ab71ee6babb692ada711d7687f","tid":261524,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Pentobarbital. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇維基寫&quot;在俄勒岡州，晚期的絕症患者可以申請利用大劑量巴比妥執行安樂死&mdash;&mdash;這藥劑可以提供無痛的死亡，但死亡的時間需要很長。一些病人幾天後才死亡，還有一些病人在失去知覺三天後最終醒了過來。&quot;藥力過左之後又死唔去應該都好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪co- potassium 囉</blockquote><br />\n但係負責執行死刑嘅都唔係專業麻醉師 如果佢地麻醉劑唔係全部注射入靜脈 之後就會有強烈嘅灼燒感 同埋靜脈注射完 再用一啲吸入性麻醉劑去確保麻醉有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32fbd7876949f8059ef181e2274fd07dc0b2673","tid":261524,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解死刑犯就以人道理由無痛死亡<br />\n但係就好多地有唔比人安樂死<br />\n普通人仲慘過死刑犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"