rprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪co- potassium 囉</blockquote><br />\n但係負責執行死刑嘅都唔係專業麻醉師 如果佢地麻醉劑唔係全部注射入靜脈 之後就會有強烈嘅灼燒感 同埋靜脈注射完 再用一啲吸入性麻醉劑去確保麻醉有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係咪O.D.架？</blockquote><br />\n唔係OD點樣致死??"},{"pid":"452a47f7f3c2d044adc5206339f178c7cc40a533","tid":261524,"uid":31758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解死刑犯就以人道理由無痛死亡<br />\n但係就好多地有唔比人安樂死<br />\n普通人仲慘過死刑犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得判左死刑之後 長年累月無義意既監禁先至係對一個死刑犯最大既拆磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你諗下佢殺左人好大機會都預左要死刑<br />\n但好似日本咁 有啲死刑犯係監倉等左十幾年都仲未行刑 明知點都要死 但剩係可以on99係個倉Fing 每日曬一陣太陽就繼續on99 諗起都覺得痴撚線"},{"pid":"d773089d2bb23d6f21c73cf226c32e66d5d600b0","tid":261524,"uid":31758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Shotgun with buckshot 以上，爆自己頭，9成9死亡率，唔會feel到痛。</blockquote><br />\n首先執屍麻煩 二來槍決係比較有尊嚴嘅死法 死刑犯會唔會唔係太啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好耐之前睇Discovery Channel話美國好似有啲州份俾死刑犯選擇槍決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8ed89eca8b6f7db883a96f7d2eba617591d28e","tid":261524,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解死刑犯就以人道理由無痛死亡<br />\n但係就好多地有唔比人安樂死<br />\n普通人仲慘過死刑犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"